cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.AR

This paper discusses the management and optimization of resources in edge computing, which involves distributed systems, networking, and system architecture. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses resource management and optimization, which falls under the categories of cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also discusses architectures and designs, which falls under the categories of cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.AR (Hardware Architecture).
